dialogs = Array[String](["It seems like you're getting a lot of press lately, right?", "I'm willing to let what happened last night slide... in exchange for a small favor.", "I own an apartment that's currently occupied by a rat. A deadbeat. Mr. Brown. I have better plans for that apartment and I'd like to get it back.", "Go steal his lease and bring it back to me. Good luck."])
